Interface RequestHandlerFactory

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface RequestHandlerFactory
extends ObjectFactory<Collection<RequestHandler>>

Responsible for creating a RequestHandler's collection. The ObjectFactory.create() will be invoked for each request. It is up to implementation to cache the requestHandler's creation.
